000Z","msg":"咩星座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39278f1a68b5135a8039578c22cddd1e45eedef2","tid":1926620,"uid":253773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T09:48:27.000Z","msg":"分手，性格不合一齊好辛苦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（不過愛能戰勝一切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"0ecc9b4923ee545d4040374eca88ffe0ab096bfe","tid":1926620,"uid":301227,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"734698fce663949c7bed42a150429726a5006bd0","tid":1926620,"uid":144522,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T09:16:06.000Z","msg":"&quot;前提我講左同邊一班人出去，我以為佢知就無答到&quot;<br />\n<br />\n唔好估下估下<br />\n寧願當佢傻仔話多佢一次知都唔好唔講<br />\n誤會好多時就係咁形成<br />\n不信任係會累積落嚟"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T09:48:35.000Z","msg":"嗯嗯 比佢估估下呢種感覺唔好受 我之後都會注意一下<br />\n其實呢件事都已經係兩個月前<br />\n之後我哋都無咩鬧交<br />\n只係問題點就黎其實有邊個唔想人氹<br />\n有次當佢話唔識氹 果時我無回應到可能就錯過左 個時機...<br />\n就好似唔識做功課 都唔會唔做㗎...<br />\n但係我唔知點同佢講好<br />\n我都好樂意去氹翻佢<br />\n不過呢家連講野溝通機會都無咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9e850d4d1cc533020b1a6edd83766e2052262f6","tid":1926620,"uid":193474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T09:48:46.000Z","msg":"雖然佢都有問題<br />\n但宜家係你唔應人先 自己做得唔好先"},{"pid":"4901000f0862ab0afa0e40c6bc5185f7af6d9301","tid":1926620,"uid":46480,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T10:15:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa9277b2e26d625df38e254603098ca1562a4324","tid":1926620,"uid":282248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1be599c7b95c4826470e41af96290443490314c7","tid":1926620,"uid":347826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0dd7f0ca8b893341f30d28fd1a7